      <front>
         <div type="tipografia" part="N" org="uniform" sample="complete">
            <p rend="writing-mode(horizontal-lr) text-orientation(sideways)" part="N">
               <s> Sculture MASTROIANNI Roma </s>
               <s> Edizione Propria N. 11 </s>
               <s> "Cromogliptica" A. Marzi - Roma  </s>
               <s> Sempre mia </s>
               <s> Toujours mienne </s>
               <s> Riproduzione interdetta </s>
               <s> Stampata in Italia </s>
            </p>
         </div>
      </front>
      <body>
         <div type="fronte" part="N" org="uniform" sample="complete">
            <figure>
               <head>Sempre mia</head>
               <figDesc> In primo piano una coppia di innamorati. Lei appoggiata ad un muretto, lui dietro che la osserva.
                  </figDesc>
            </figure>
         </div>
         <div type="retro">
            <div type="message">
               <opener>
                  <dateline>
                     <lb/>
                     <s>            30/11-1916</s>
                  </dateline>
               </opener>
               <div type="postcard-body">
                  <p>
                     <lb/>            (ore 12) <lb/>            Oliva,<lb/>            È il tuo Giovannino che t'invoca, <lb/>            che t'ama ardentemente, divinamente!<lb/>            Quando ci sarà concesfo d'amarci come <lb/>            proprio il nostro cuore ci detta? Quando io<lb/>            soavemente potrò adagiare il mio capo<lb/>            ormai stordito tanto, felicemente sul <lb/>            tuo purisfimo grembo e dormire <lb/>            come il fanciullo lieto suole, tran-<lb/>            quillo, sotto lo sguardo vigile della<lb/>            madre? Io ti voglio tanto, tanto <lb/>            lume, un mondo di lume puro ardente.<lb/>            E tu, al tuo Giovannino???<lb/>            Pensa un pochino al tuo Giovan-<lb/>            nino?!!  </p>
                  <p type="fronte"/>
               </div>
               <closer>
                  <s>
                     <lb/>Un bacio affettuoso <lb/>con tutto il trasporto dell'anima <lb/>mia tuo <lb/>
                     <signed>
                        <persName>
                           <forename ref="Giovannino">Giovannino</forename>
                        </persName>
                     </signed>
                  </s>
               </closer>
            </div>
            <div type="postmark-postage">
               <ab/>
            </div>
            <div type="secondamano">
               <ab type="paratext" part="N">
                  <add>
                     <num type="cardinal"> 37 </num>
                  </add>
               </ab>
            </div>
         </div>
      </body>
